PN,31601
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1781194282
OL,3,CSole survivor of Air India crash calls
OL,4,Cfor transparency and answers 12 months
OL,5,Con
OL,7,FThe sole survivor of the Air India
OL,8,Fplane crash that killed 241 people has
OL,9,Fcalled for "honesty, transparency and
OL,10,Fanswers" a year on from the disaster.
OL,12,FBriton Vishwash Kumar Ramesh said he
OL,13,Fcontinued to "live with the
OL,14,Fsignificant psychological scars"
OL,15,Ffollowing the death of his brother in
OL,16,Fthe crash in June last year.
OL,26,@qD@LOUrD@HO]uD@NOUvD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1781194282
OL,3,CSole survivor of Air India crash calls
OL,4,Cfor transparency and answers 12 months
OL,5,Con
OL,7,FThe London-bound Boeing 787 Dreamliner
OL,8,Fsmashed into a medical college shortly
OL,9,Fafter taking off from Ahmedabad
OL,10,FAirport, killing everyone on board
OL,11,Fother than 39-year-old Mr Ramesh.
OL,13,FSome 169 Indian passengers and 52
OL,14,FBritish nationals were killed, making
OL,15,Fit one of the deadliest plane crashes
OL,16,Fin terms of the number of British
OL,17,Ffatalities.
OL,19,FBesides those on board flight AI171,
OL,20,Fanother 19 people also died and 67
OL,21,Fwere seriously injured.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1781194282
OL,3,CSole survivor of Air India crash calls
OL,4,Cfor transparency and answers 12 months
OL,5,Con
OL,7,FMr Ramesh, who has lived in Leicester
OL,8,Ffor more than 20 years, previously
OL,9,Fsaid the death of his brother Ajay
OL,10,F"took all my happiness" after
OL,11,Fdescribing it as a "miracle" that he
OL,12,Fsurvived.
OL,14,FIn a short statement 12 months on from
OL,15,Fthe crash, he told the Press
OL,16,FAssociation: "What many people perhaps
OL,17,Fdon't fully appreciate is that the
OL,18,Ftrauma didn't end on the day of the
OL,19,Fdisaster.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@WO]sD@TOUsD@\O]xD@NOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1781194282
OL,3,CSole survivor of Air India crash calls
OL,4,Cfor transparency and answers 12 months
OL,5,Con
OL,7,F"I live with the significant
OL,8,Fpsychological scars, the loss of my
OL,9,Fbrother, and the constant unanswered
OL,10,Fquestions around how and why this
OL,11,Fhappened.
OL,13,F"I know those questions are not just
OL,14,Fon my mind ` they are on the minds of
OL,15,Fevery affected family.
OL,17,F"More than anything, people need
OL,18,Fhonesty, transparency and answers.
OL,19,FNothing will ever change what
OL,20,Fhappened, but families deserve
OL,21,Fclarity."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUyD@AOU}D@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1781194282
OL,3,CSole survivor of Air India crash calls
OL,4,Cfor transparency and answers 12 months
OL,5,Con
OL,7,FInvestigators have yet to publish
OL,8,Ftheir final findings into the cause of
OL,9,Fthe crash.
OL,11,FA preliminary report into the incident
OL,12,Ffrom India's Aircraft Accident
OL,13,FInvestigation Bureau found both of the
OL,14,Fplane's fuel switches moved to the
OL,15,F"cut-off" position "immediately" after
OL,16,Ftake-off, stopping fuel supply to the
OL,17,Fengine.
OL,19,FMr Ramesh met with Air Accident
OL,20,FInvestigators in Ahmedabad in March,
OL,21,Fhis representative Sanjiv Patel said.
OL,26,@wD@AOUwD@IO]wD@TOUwD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1781194282
OL,3,CSole survivor of Air India crash calls
OL,4,Cfor transparency and answers 12 months
OL,5,Con
OL,7,FMr Patel said the crash survivor has
OL,8,Fto date received #21,500 from Air
OL,9,FIndia to support his wife and five-
OL,10,Fyear-old son ` an interim payment
OL,11,Fprovided to all families who lost
OL,12,Floved ones in the disaster.
OL,14,FHe told the Press Association: "He
OL,15,Fcontinues to struggle physically,
OL,16,Fpsychologically and financially.
OL,18,F"We've repeatedly asked to meet the
OL,19,Fchief executive of Air India but that
OL,20,Fhas not happened.
OL,26,@vD@`OUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1781194282
OL,3,CSole survivor of Air India crash calls
OL,4,Cfor transparency and answers 12 months
OL,5,Con
OL,7,F"We recently met with executives of
OL,8,FAir India and representatives
OL,9,Fconnected to the Tata Group.
OL,11,F"Those discussions were constructive
OL,12,Fand have resulted in some positive
OL,13,Fprogress, although a number of
OL,14,Fimportant issues remain under
OL,15,Fdiscussion.
OL,17,F"The reality is that Viswash and his
OL,18,Ffamily continue to face significant
OL,19,Ffinancial hardship.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1781194282
OL,3,CSole survivor of Air India crash calls
OL,4,Cfor transparency and answers 12 months
OL,5,Con
OL,7,F"Due to the physical and psychological
OL,8,Fimpact of the crash he has been unable
OL,9,Fto return to work and support his
OL,10,Ffamily in the way he once did, leaving
OL,11,Fthem currently living on less than
OL,12,F#1,000 per month.
OL,14,F"They're not alone. Despite one of the
OL,15,Fworst aviation disasters involving
OL,16,FBritish citizens in recent years,
OL,17,Fneither Viswash nor many of the
OL,18,Faffected families we have spoken to
OL,19,Fhave received any direct contact or
OL,20,Ftailored support from the UK
OL,21,FGovernment."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU}D@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1781194282
OL,3,CSole survivor of Air India crash calls
OL,4,Cfor transparency and answers 12 months
OL,5,Con
OL,7,FMr Ramesh is taking civil action
OL,8,Ffollowing the crash, with his
OL,9,Fsolicitors saying: "We will be
OL,10,Fexamining every detail of the air
OL,11,Faccident investigations and expecting
OL,12,Fall parties involved to act
OL,13,Fappropriately to any findings of
OL,14,Ffault, failure or negligence."
OL,16,FSolicitor Paul McClorry from Hudgell
OL,17,FSolicitors said civil claims are being
OL,18,Fconsidered against a number of
OL,19,Fpotential defendants.
OL,26,@qD@TOUvD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1781194282
OL,3,CSole survivor of Air India crash calls
OL,4,Cfor transparency and answers 12 months
OL,5,Con
OL,7,FHe said in a statement: "We've had
OL,8,Fsignificant dialogue with the legal
OL,9,Frepresentatives for Air India and they
OL,10,Fhave been very cooperative in recent
OL,11,Ftimes, providing some initial funding
OL,12,Ffor much needed physical and
OL,13,Fpsychological rehabilitation support.
OL,15,F"We are awaiting the findings of the
OL,16,Finvestigations, and we should finally
OL,17,Fstart to see some clarity as to how
OL,18,Fand why this awful disaster happened,
OL,19,Fand, crucially, how it could have been
OL,20,Favoided.
OL,26,@oD@YOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1781194282
OL,3,CSole survivor of Air India crash calls
OL,4,Cfor transparency and answers 12 months
OL,5,Con
OL,7,F"Lessons clearly must be learnt, and
OL,8,Ffor that to happen there needs to be
OL,9,Fcomplete transparency and a
OL,10,Fwillingness to accept responsibility."
OL,12,FThe Foreign Office have been
OL,13,Fapproached for comment.
OL,15,FA spokesperson for Air India said:
OL,16,F"Air India remains committed to
OL,17,Fsupporting every individual impacted
OL,18,Fby the AI171 tragedy with care and
OL,19,Fcompassion.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@fO]xD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1781194282
OL,3,CSole survivor of Air India crash calls
OL,4,Cfor transparency and answers 12 months
OL,5,Con
OL,7,F"While we cannot discuss the specifics
OL,8,Fof any individual case,
OL,9,Frepresentatives from Air India and the
OL,10,FTata Group met with Mr Ramesh and had
OL,11,Fa constructive and meaningful
OL,12,Fengagement.
OL,14,F"The discussions provided insight into
OL,15,FMr Ramesh's needs and concerns,
OL,16,Fenabling a clearer understanding of
OL,17,Fhow best to support him.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31613
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1781194282
OL,3,CSole survivor of Air India crash calls
OL,4,Cfor transparency and answers 12 months
OL,5,Con
OL,7,F"We remain in close contact with Mr
OL,8,FRamesh and his representatives and are
OL,9,Factively working to ensure that
OL,10,Fappropriate support continues to be
OL,11,Fextended to him."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@QO]
